OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fnight to come with patches of high
OL,7,Fcloud and clear spells. A few isolated
OL,8,Fshowers possible, but a much more
OL,9,Fcomfortable night for many compare to
OL,10,Frecent nights.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FLow cloud to start with, but
OL,13,Flifting through the morning and into
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Isolated showers
OL,15,Fdeveloping, with sunny spells in
OL,16,Fbetween. Warm, but cooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
